channel.title: You'll want to check this out
channel.description:
Hey! I am back to RSPS after being away from them for college. I had quite a bit of time to study more coding while studying software dev. in school!
I wanted to become part of a dev team for a rsps. I can code and I can host 24/7 via VPS. PM me your skype username, and we can talk from there. Have a great day! :)

I’m wanting to go to school for software development. Is there any success behind a degree with it or is it a hit or miss?
[/quote]If you are expecting to get a job with your degree, maybe. But if you don’t show intiative, intelligence, teamwork, etc. then you will not get a good job.[/quote]
